name: Trump Digital Trading Cards Series 2
description:
Introducing Series 2 of Trump Digital Trading Cards!

Are you ready to add to your collection of Official Trump Digital Trading Cards? Series 2 is here, featuring even more incredible art inspired by some of the most iconic moments from Trump's time as a public figure.

Series 2 includes Limited One-of-Ones, Autographed Cards, and even more extraordinary finds to add to your collection. From Rockstars to Monster Truckers, the one-of-a-kind designs offer something for every collector.

Head to [CollectTrumpCards.com](http://collecttrumpcards.com/) to learn more about Series 2 now. Make sure to follow us at @CollectTrump on Twitter and Truth Social for the latest updates on this exciting collection.

Before purchasing any Trump Digital Trading Cards, please read the Terms and Conditions (bit.ly/3GLdD1j) and the owners agreement specific to each NFT (bit.ly/3ol6SNu) carefully to ensure you understand your rights and any restrictions that apply.

Start or continue collecting today!
